        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Joshua 15:13-14",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The LXX. have, “Hebron came forth against Judah.” For later references to Hebron, see ",
        "children": []
